## Implementation Details

### Database Schema
- match_actions: Records user like/pass/super_like actions
- mutual_matches: Cached mutual match records
- match_preferences: User matching preferences

### Matching Algorithms

1. User-to-User Matching (Weighted Scoring):
   - Fitness level similarity: 20%
   - Shared interests: 30%
   - Geographic proximity: 25%
   - Schedule compatibility: 20%
   - Past interactions: 5%

2. User-to-Class Matching (Weighted Scoring):
   - Fitness interests match: 35%
   - Appropriate intensity: 25%
   - Schedule fit: 20%
   - Location convenience: 15%
   - Price range: 5%

### API Endpoints Implemented

1. GET /api/v1/matches/partners - Find workout partners
2. GET /api/v1/matches/classes - Get class recommendations
3. GET /api/v1/matches/mutual - List mutual matches
4. POST /api/v1/matches/action - Record match actions

